  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic tibial tray fixation credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA-based prediction of tibial tray micromotion under physiological loading for a cementless total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case fixation failure conditions for a Class II orthopedic device at Model Risk Level 3. Full 13-factor assessment: all factors assessed with required and achieved levels documented, provenance chain complete to foundational experimental datasets.",
